td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Red<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarbeck\" title=\"House Tarbeck\">House Tarbeck</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_242_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">242&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Tarbeck_Hall\" title=\"Tarbeck Hall\">Tarbeck Hall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Tarbeck_Hall\" title=\"Tarbeck Hall\">Tarbeck Hall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Walderan_Tarbeck\" title=\"Walderan Tarbeck\">Walderan Tarbeck</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Reyne\" title=\"Ellyn Reyne\">Ellyn Reyne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tion Tarbeck</b>, nicknamed <b>the Red</b>, was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarbeck\" title=\"House Tarbeck\">House Tarbeck</a>. He was the son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walderan_Tarbeck\" title=\"Walderan Tarbeck\">Walderan Tarbeck</a> by his third wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Reyne\" title=\"Ellyn Reyne\">Ellyn Reyne</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tion_Tarbeck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, Tion had red hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tion_Tarbeck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, Ellyn Reyne <a href=\"/index.php/Named_after\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named after\">named</a> her son after the late <a href=\"/index.php/Tion_Lannister\" title=\"Tion Lannister\">Tion Lannister</a>, Ellyn's first husband, as an attack against <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Lord of Casterly Rock\">Lord of Casterly Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Tion Tarbeck died in the collapse of <a href=\"/index.php/Tarbeck_Hall\" title=\"Tarbeck Hall\">Tarbeck Hall</a>, during <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Reyne-Tarbeck_revolt\" title=\"Reyne-Tarbeck revolt\">suppression</a> of Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Reyne\" title=\"House Reyne\">Reyne</a> and Tarbeck.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tion_Tarbeck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tion had two sisters and several half-siblings.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />two wives</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Walderan_Tarbeck\" title=\"Walderan Tarbeck\">Walderan</a><br /><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;Note 1&#93;</a></sup></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Reyne\" title=\"Ellyn Reyne\">Ellyn<br />Reyne</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px